{"lemma":"لَبَّةٌ","slug":"لَبَّةٌ","root":"ل.ب.ب","root_slug":"ل-ب-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ل-ب-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n37429"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n37429","headword_ar":"لَبَّةٌ","root":"lb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lababN","text_ar":"لَبَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stabbing-place in an animal;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"middle of the breast:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pit above the breast, between the collar-bones; the place where camels are stabbed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lab~ahu","text_ar":"لَبَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bones"},{"kind":"text","text":"[probably a mistake for the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part next above the bones"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that are above the breast, and below the throat, between the collar-bones, where camels are stabbed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"he who says that it is the pit in the throat errs: (IKt:) [for it is just beneath the throat:] pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lab~aAtN","text_ar":"لَبَّاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"libaAbN","text_ar":"لِبَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and of the latter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^alobaAbN","text_ar":"اَلْبَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) Also, both words, (the latter ↓ accord. to the S and K, and the former accord. to the TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mutalab~abN","text_ar":"مُتَلَبَّبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of the breast where the necklace"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collar lies,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hangs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) in anything; (S;) [i. e., in a human being or a beast:] or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pit above it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lababN","text_ar":"لَبَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^alobaAbN","text_ar":"اَلْبَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) Lh mentions the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahaA laHasanahu","text_ar":"اـِنَّهَا لَحَسَنَهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~ab~aAti","text_ar":"اللَّبَّاتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily she is beautiful in the upper part of the breast"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: as though the sing. were applied to each portion of it, and the pl. formed to denote the whole. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["L","IKt","S","TA","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}